    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A thermoplastic resin derived by the polymerization of vinyl chloride, used for thin coatings, insulation, and pipes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
